---
title: Easy Tunisian Lamb & Rapid Spinach Rice with Tomato Salsa & Currants
description: Introduce your tastebuds to the incredible flavour of Tunisian seasoning, a North African spice that really packs a punch. Sitting
on a bed of spinach rice that's studded with currants and topped with yoghurt, this tender lamb dish offers a depth of flavour
and a speedy turnaround time that's sure to knock your socks off.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
